new-passinfo-passengers__hint__text: If you buy a ticket using a foreign passport, please enter your last name and first name as written in your document (using Latin letters). If your document contains Cyrillic letters, our system transliterates them automatically, because the reservation system data is kept only in Latin letters. Generally you may do up to three(3) mistakes when entering your last name and first name. But we suggest you dont do any.
